definition: to hit (the mark)/to be hit by/to suffer/to win (a prize, a lottery)
car/vehicle/CL:輛|辆[liang4]/machine/to shape with a lathe/Kangxi radical 159

sentences.english: Boeing ( BA - news - people ) can sell more planes than Airbus.
sentences.chinese: 波音公司可以比空中客車賣出更多的飛機。

sentences.english: Airbus delivered 18 of its A380 superjumbo last year.
sentences.chinese: 空中客車交付18架其A380超巨型飛機去年。

sentences.english: Airbus has had delays with its huge, new A-Three-Eighty passenger plane.
sentences.chinese: 因此空中客車推遲了新款巨型A380客機的生產。

sentences.english: Airbus had also advised its customers to replace the sensors.
sentences.chinese: 空中客車也建議它的客戶更換傳感器。

sentences.english: The crash was the second involving an Airbus aircraft in recent weeks.
sentences.chinese: 這次空難是最近幾周空中客車飛機的第二次事故。
